        dataSource.setUser( &quot;scott&quot; );
        dataSource.setPassword( &quot;tiger&quot; );
        return dataSource;
    }
```

Retain that `DataSource` object in your app. When needing a database connection, call `DataSource#getConnection`. 

```java
        String sql = &quot;SELECT name_ from  user_ ; &quot; ;
